    "by the Act of June 25, 1948 (ch. 645, 62 Stat. 683). The words \"section 9 of act August 2, "
    "1882 (22 Stat. 189)\" are omitted because that law was repealed by section 4(b) of Public Law "
    "98–89 (Aug. 26, 1983, 97 Stat. 600)."
)
